commit.message:
Makefile.in: Remove the Project Manager from the GNAT tools.

2017-09-06  Vincent Celier  <celier@adacore.com>

        * gcc-interface/Makefile.in: Remove the Project Manager from the GNAT
	tools.

From-SVN: r251787
